{
  "page": "Young John Mudd",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/index.php/Old_John_Mudd\" title=\"Old John Mudd\">Old John Mudd</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/50px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/75px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/100px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />John Mudd</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/50px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/75px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/100px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:John_Mudd_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"John Mudd TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/bf/John_Mudd_TheMico.jpg/350px-John_Mudd_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"/images/b/bf/John_Mudd_TheMico.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nYoung John Mudd</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Serjeant\" title=\"Serjeant\">Serjeant</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ser\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ser\">Ser</a> <small>(allegedly)</small></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Old_John_Mudd\" title=\"Old John Mudd\">Old John Mudd</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Young John Mudd</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> in service to the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>. He holds the rank of serjeant<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and claims to be a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character_and_Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character and Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_John\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by John</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_John\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about John</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_and_Appearance\">Character and Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character and Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>John has brown skin and wears brown clothes. He decorates his ears with golden coins. He has scars and weathered face. John is a brusque, brutal man who wields sword and dagger. He is not well spoken. He is skilled with <a href=\"/index.php/Dice\" title=\"Dice\">dice</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Although he is not a young man, John is known as Young John because his father, <a href=\"/index.php/Old_John_Mudd\" title=\"Old John Mudd\">Old John Mudd</a>, was also a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Their surname is of a house that had once loomed large in the histories of the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mudd\" title=\"House Mudd\">House Mudd</a> ruled as <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">Kings of the Rivers and the Hills</a> thousands of years ago until their line was extinguished with the death of King <a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_V_Mudd\" title=\"Tristifer V Mudd\">Tristifer V Mudd</a> at the hands of the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> He may or may not be of House Mudd, as in the free companies a man can call himself whatever he chooses, and not all such names are genuine.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> He may also be related to another serjeant in the company, <a href=\"/index.php/Lorimas_Mudd\" title=\"Lorimas Mudd\">Lorimas Mudd</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>John may have been present during <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a>'s rendezvous with the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a> three miles south of <a href=\"/index.php/Volon_Therys\" title=\"Volon Therys\">Volon Therys</a>, as Jon notices that a Mudd is present during the meeting. Like the rest of the company, he swears his allegiance to <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a> before they <a href=\"/index.php/Landing_of_the_Golden_Company\" title=\"Landing of the Golden Company\">invade Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Young John Mudd and <a href=\"/index.php/Chain\" title=\"Chain\">Chain</a> hold <a href=\"/index.php/Mistwood\" title=\"Mistwood\">Mistwood</a> for the Golden Company. They keep Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Mary_Mertyns\" title=\"Mary Mertyns\">Mary Mertyns</a> under house arrest and host <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a>'s party for a night.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_John\">Quotes by John</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by John\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>We serve <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">your rightful king</a>, old crone.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;John to <a href=\"/index.php/Mary_Mertyns\" title=\"Mary Mertyns\">Mary Mertyns</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_John\">Quotes about John</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about John\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mudd\" title=\"House Mudd\">Mudds</a> had been <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">kings up by the Trident</a> a thousand years ago, she knew, but there was nothing royal about this one. Nor was he particularly young, but it seemed his father had also served in the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>, where he had been known as <a href=\"/index.php/Old_John_Mudd\" title=\"Old John Mudd\">Old John Mudd</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Young_John_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ar2-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-4\">2.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-5\">2.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_II_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne II</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, The Lost Lord.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, Catelyn V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403115632\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.123 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.381 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1021/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11166/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 11841/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1713/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3297/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.240/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.79 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  358.490      1 -total\n 81.55%  292.339      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 81.10%  290.722      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.90%   39.080      1 Template:Distinguish\n  8.01%   28.724     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.00%   17.916      6 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.30%   15.428      6 Temp